about.summary: Functions to fit finite mixture of scale mixture of skew-normal (FM-SMSN) distributions.

name: r-mixsmsn
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.1-5' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mixsmsn
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/mixsmsn_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/mixsmsn/mixsmsn_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fc783d81a2c7734ca85550248b7cce6a9b8b228e539d700e9a58e35e0ed43e78

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1001
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mvtnorm >=0.9_9
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mvtnorm >=0.9_9

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('mixsmsn')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('mixsmsn')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=mixsmsn
  license: GPL (>= 2.0)
  summary: Functions to fit finite mixture of scale mixture of skew-normal (FM-SMSN) distributions.
  license_family: GPL3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
